name: CompositeMap_containsKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the containsKey method in the CompositeMap class.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyPresentInFirstMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns true when the key is present in the first map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyPresentInSecondMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns true when the key is present in the second map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyNotPresent
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns false when the key is not present in any map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterAddingNewMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns true after adding a new map with the key.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterRemovingKey
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns false after removing the key from the map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterRemovingCompositedMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsKey method returns false after removing a composited map containing the key.
